      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just walking in circles lately. every time i think i finally got my life together, like i actually have a handle on things, something just pulls the rug out from under me. it’s the same pattern every single time. i try so hard to fix things but i just end up right back where i started. it's exhausting.",
